title: Sonata Antartika - Sonata In Troll Minor
description:
Sonata Antartika is a melodic death metal/power metal/metalcore/comedy metal band from Athens, Greece.

They kicked off by covering several well-known anime intros and greek pop-folk songs and they quickly moved on to creating original songs, leading to the recording of a full-length album, featuring well-known artists from the greek metal scene.

This is Sonata Antartika's first attempt at recording an album and it has already sold over 45.000.000 million copies in Greece alone. Being critically acclaimed all over the globe, it is estimated that the album's worldwide sales have exceeded 7 billion copies, while it is distributed as part of NATO's humanitarian actions in Iraq, Afghanistan, Yugoslavia and Serbia.
